{% extends 'layout.html.j2' %}

{% import '_pagination.html.j2' as pagination %}

{% block title %}Advanced Search - {{ super() }}{% endblock %}

{% block header %}
   <header>
      <div class="container">
         <h1>Advanced Search</h1>
      </div>
   </header>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
   <main class="container">
      <div class="row">
         <form class="col-md-4">
            <div class="form-group">
               <label class="control-label sr-only" for="shelfmark">Shelfmark</label>
               <input type="search" id="shelfmark" placeholder="Shelfmark" name="shelfmark" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
               <label class="control-label sr-only" for="playwright">Playwright</label>
               <input type="search" id="playwright" placeholder="Playwright" name="playwright" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
               <label class="control-label sr-only" for="play">Play</label>
               <input type="search" id="play" placeholder="Play" name="play" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
               <label class="control-label sr-only" for="character">Character</label>
               <input type="search" id="character" placeholder="Character" name="character" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
               <label class="control-label sr-only" for="keyword">Keyword</label>
               <input type="search" id="keyword" placeholder="Keyword" name="keyword" class="form-control">
            </div>
            <div class="btn-row">
               <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                  <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></i>
                  <span>Search</span>
               </button>
            </div>
         </form>
         <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="text-right toolbar">
               {{ pagination.pagination(10, 1, 2) }}
               <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="manuscript display text">
                  <button type="button" id="showNormalized" class="btn btn-default active">Normalized</button>
                  <button type="button" id="showOriginal" class="btn btn-default">Original</button>
               </div>
            </div>


         <div id="extractList" class="extract-list show-normalized">
            <div class="extract">
               <div class="original">
                  <blockquote>
                     <p>I keepemy horse, I keepe my whore, <br>I havenowealth, yet I’me poore. <br>I travellall theworld about, <br>And yet was borne to ne’re a foot. <br>w<sup>th</sup> partridge plump, &amp; woodcocke fine, <br>At midnight oft I use to dine. <br>And when my whore is out of case, <br>My hostesse daughter takes her place. <br>The maids sit up, &amp; watch their turnes, <br>If I stay late the tapster mournes. <br>The cooke-maid will not yeild to sin, <br>Though tempted by the Chamberlin <br>And when I knocke, oh!how theyhustle, <br>The Ostler yawns, the Geldings justle. <br>And then I call bring forth my horse, S<sup>r</sup> <br>And aftercomes, deliver your purse, S<sup>r</sup>. </p>
                  </blockquote>
               </div>
               <div class="normalized">
                  <blockquote>
                     <p>I keepmy horse, I keep my whore, <br>I takenorents, yet  am not   poore . <br>I travelall theland about, <br>And yet was born to ne’re a foot. <br>with partridge plump, with woodcocke fine, <br>I do midnight  often  I use to dine. <br>And if my whore be not in case, <br>My hostess' daughter takes her place. <br>The maids sit up, &amp; watch their turns, <br>If I stay long the tapster mourns. <br>The cook-maid has no mind to sin, <br>Though tempted by the Chamberlin <br> But  when I knock, O howhow theybustle, <br>The Ostler yawns, the Geldings justle. <br>If maid but sleep, O how they curse her! <br>And all thiscomes, deliver your purse, Sir.</p>
                  </blockquote>
               </div>

               <div class="extract-citation">
                  <div>
                     <span>Folger MS V.a.262</span> (
                     <span>f. 5v</span>)</div>
                  <div>by
                     <span>Lady Macbeth</span> in
                     <span>
                        <em>Macbeth</em>
                     </span> (
                     <span>Shakespeare</span>)</div>
               </div>
            </div>


            <div class="extract">
               <div class="original">
                  <span class="label">By Ben Jonson</span>
                  <blockquote>
                     <p>Still to be neat, still to be drest, <br>As you were goeing to a feast; <br>Still to be pouder'd, still pfum'd <br>Ladie it is to be presum'd <br>Though arts hid causes are not found <br>All is not sweete, all is not sound.  <br>Give me alooke, give me a face <br>That makessimplicitie a grace: <br>Roabelooselyhanging, hayre as free. <br>Such sweet neglect more taketh me. <br>Thenallthe spurious feats of art <br>Theyplease mine eyes, but not my hart.</p>
                  </blockquote>
